  <original-body>This route:

map.namespace 'api', :path_prefix =&gt; '' do |api|
  api.route 'inventory', :controller =&gt; &quot;products&quot;, :action =&gt; 'inventory'
end

Generates &quot;//inventory&quot; as path and it should generate &quot;/inventory&quot;.

The submitted patch was tested on the 2.2-stable branch.</original-body>
